title: Super Bowl winners & losers
itunes:title: Super Bowl winners & losers
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Colleen Wolfe – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL, including Cam Newton’s response to his Super Bowl critics, and reports that Browns quarterback Johnny Manziel showed up drunk to a team practice in December. Then, the heroes break down their winners and losers of Super Bowl 50, and debate whether or not Marshawn Lynch is a Hall of Famer.
